<br>
Baseball bats?  Do you know how it honestly feels to be after being on the receiving end of a swing of the baseball bat?  I took a swing to the ribs once in gym class back in high school, I wasn't breathing easy for the next week.<br>
<br>
Put some honest thought into what you are doing and what reprecussions you are willing to face.  I wouldn't be risking my now spotless criminal record in order to pay back a $1k theft.  An assault charge on your record can and will be damaging.  If you are under the age of 18, chances are that you will be spending a night or two in a Juvenile Detention Center(JDC) if you do beat them to the extent that most have suggested.<br>
<br>
First thing that happens upon entry to a JDC is you get strip and cavity searched.  You feel like having essentially a prison guard shove his gloved hand up your ass to search for drugs/weapons?  Maybe you do.<br>
<br>
Take a good long look at your options.  Either do something that they can't trace back to you or bring in a parent, teacher, and/or representative of the law to retrieve the goods stolen.<br>
